        available government data into readable news articles. We aggregate data from official U.S.
        government sources including the Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC), Food and Drug
        Administration (FDA), National Highway Traffic Safety Administration (NHTSA), National Oceanic
        and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), and Federal Emergency
        Management Agency (FEMA).
      </p>

      <h2>AI-Generated Content Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
