      <ul>
        <li>Articles may contain AI-introduced inaccuracies in phrasing, context, or interpretation</li>
        <li>Articles are not written or reviewed by human journalists</li>
        <li>The original government source data is always linked for verification</li>
        <li>Articles should be considered <strong>summaries</strong> of official data, not authoritative reporting</li>
      </ul>
