        <li>A substitute for official recall notices or safety warnings</li>
        <li>Emergency notification or early warning services</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <strong>In any emergency, always call 911 or your local emergency number.</strong> Do not
        rely on {SITE_NAME} for emergency information. Our content may be delayed from the original
        government publication by minutes to hours.
      </p>

